@startuml

title Pigeon Swarm - Advanced Sync Flow

actor "Local User" as User

box "Local Node"
participant "Application Use Case" as UseCase
participant "Domain Model" as Domain
database "MongoDB\nLocal Read/Write Index" as Mongo
participant "IPFS / Helia\nImmutable Blobs" as IPFS
participant "DHT\nHead Discovery" as DHT
participant "DomainEventPublisher" as EventPublisher
participant "MessageBus\nHelia PubSub Adapter" as PubSub
participant "Sync Engine" as Sync
end box

box "Remote Node"
participant "Remote PubSub" as RPubSub
participant "Remote Sync Engine" as RSync
database "Remote MongoDB" as RMongo
participant "Remote IPFS" as RIPFS
participant "Remote DHT" as RDHT
end box

== Identity Publication ==

User -> UseCase : update profile or networks
UseCase -> Domain : create next Identity
Domain -> Domain : sign canonical payload
UseCase -> IPFS : store immutable identity document
IPFS --> UseCase : identity CID
UseCase -> Mongo : store local identity metadata
UseCase -> DHT : put identity CID hint
UseCase -> EventPublisher : publish IdentityWasPublished
EventPublisher -> PubSub : adapter publishes domain event

PubSub -> RPubSub : gossip identity CID
RPubSub -> RSync : handle announcement
RSync -> RIPFS : fetch identity document
RIPFS --> RSync : identity document
RSync -> RSync : validate signature, version and previous CID
RSync -> RMongo : store local identity metadata

== 1to1 Conversation Creation ==

User -> UseCase : start chat with identity
UseCase -> Mongo : find local owner identity
UseCase -> DHT : discover remote identity CIDs if needed
UseCase -> IPFS : fetch missing identity documents
UseCase -> Domain : create OneToOneConversation
Domain -> Domain : derive deterministic conversation id
UseCase -> Mongo : save conversation aggregate metadata
UseCase -> PubSub : subscribe conversation topic

== Message Publication ==

User -> UseCase : send message
UseCase -> Domain : load Conversation aggregate
UseCase -> Domain : record MessageSent event
Domain -> Domain : encrypt payload and sign event
UseCase -> IPFS : store dependent event blob
IPFS --> UseCase : event CID
UseCase -> Mongo : store conversation event metadata
UseCase -> EventPublisher : publish ConversationMessageWasSent
EventPublisher -> PubSub : adapter publishes domain event

PubSub -> RPubSub : gossip message
RPubSub -> RSync : handle domain event
RSync -> RMongo : check event id
alt missing event
  RSync -> RIPFS : fetch event CID
  RIPFS --> RSync : event blob
  RSync -> RSync : load Conversation and validate dependent event
  RSync -> RMongo : store conversation event metadata
  RSync -> RPubSub : re-gossip if useful
end

== Edit or Delete ==

User -> UseCase : edit or delete message
UseCase -> Domain : load Conversation aggregate
UseCase -> Domain : record MessageEdited or MessageDeleted
Domain -> Domain : target original event id
Domain -> Domain : sign compensating event
UseCase -> IPFS : store immutable edit/delete event
IPFS --> UseCase : event CID
UseCase -> Mongo : store conversation event metadata
UseCase -> EventPublisher : publish conversation domain event
EventPublisher -> PubSub : adapter publishes domain event

== Anti Entropy Recovery ==

Sync -> PubSub : request known conversation events
PubSub -> RPubSub : SyncRequest(conversationId, knownEventIds)
RPubSub -> RSync : compare known events
RSync -> RMongo : find missing event CIDs
RSync -> RPubSub : SyncResponse(CIDs)
RPubSub -> Sync : response
Sync -> IPFS : fetch missing event blobs
Sync -> Sync : load Conversation, validate and merge
Sync -> Mongo : store conversation event metadata

@enduml
